text: Jean Nakouzi (born 19 May 1947) is a Lebanese wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 57 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Lebanese male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Lebanon Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Beirut
